{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给郭士逵的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给郭士逵的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年3月14日）士逵先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年十月五日来信收到，迟复为歉。先生处境困难，深为系念。工作问题，仍以就近设法等侯机会为宜，不宜远出省外，徒劳往返。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺问近安！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年三月十四日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]郭士逵（1899—1960），湖南韶山银田人，后迁居湖南湘潭良湖乡，农民。1925年毛泽东在韶山一带开展农民运动时，遭湖南军阀赵恒惕通缉，郭士逵曾帮助他脱险。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":3,"day":14}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":235,"page_end":235},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}